Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.30,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember this! I'll beat your ass at the dojo tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:47.31,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with her? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.31,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.40,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Jinguji-san is at fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.44,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.65,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you can get changed in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.34,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.65,RM main 2,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to apologize?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:06.55,RM main 2,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:09.29,RM main 2,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, calm down you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.66,RM main 2,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.54,RM main 2,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.15,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,They're rather loud, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.39,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:36.94,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have screamed like that in front of that Kota boy like you did just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:38.90,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:43.04,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,You just won't get how much it hurts to not be viewed as a member of the opposite sex...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:45.32,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,...until you experience it first-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:50.64,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Not being seen as a member of the opposite sex...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.64,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Yako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:58.69,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's what hurt Kota-kun's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:02.01,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you think, Komachi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:06.14,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I think it goes both ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.95,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:15.29,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu-chan, do you want to go check out the Goldfish Scoop over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.71,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.37,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go buy something. You guys go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:21.86,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lose you, Amahara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:24.65,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kid, I won't get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:31.37,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,These kids have a lot on their minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:37.29,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, he said that he got called in to his office...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.04,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll make it in time for the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:42.88,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Ah, watching fireworks with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.56,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:50.67,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but you are so much more beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:54.50,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Um... My tits are gonna pop out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:55.67,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:59.28,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,My hands will be your bra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.85,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,What would I do if that actually happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:09.95,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.91,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone?! Were did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:15.96,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, look at these goldfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:17.83,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,They're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.83,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Their tails sure are long!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.75,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Want to give it a go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.33,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Kota...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.97,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,You should talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:29.58,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:32.43,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:35.85,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Men are stubborn creatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.30,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,we have a hard time apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:39.40,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Cat-eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.23,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:45.78,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Give him a chance too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.71,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:53.15,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you, Yako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:54.10,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.66,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I think so too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:58.35,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.22,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,He's your childhood friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:03.06,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,You should treasure him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:09.90,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Dwelling on it like this really isn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.88,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:12.68,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:16.10,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they can work things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.16,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.79,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why are you wearing a mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.48,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,That's gonna be kept a secret from you, Hayama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.57,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.82,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Just come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:34.71,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop going off on your own guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.41,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.10,RM main 2,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're good at this, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:41.92,RM main 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:46.67,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-san didn't see your perverted face while you were looking at her, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.67,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll charge you for it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.06,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,H-How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.18,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.80,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you an old man in a sales shop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:59.27,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Class Rep, summer is the season where girls open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.04,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try asking Hayama out on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:05.29,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're completely red again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.99,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,You really are fun to tease!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.46,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,They really get along well, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:15.04,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's because they're in the same class?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.02,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:20.11,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! There's a lot of them right here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.87,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one do you like, Haruka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:24.50,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't bother you, Nayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:25.92,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:26.92,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.88,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about Komachi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.76,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Haruka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:35.42,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.39,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,This really sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.41,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to do it over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:43.87,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Haruka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:44.91,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:50.96,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fix your bra first, so I'm gonna stick my hands in, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:51.57,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.13,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Did I hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:56.70,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:00.41,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.71,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even louder than when we did the bra fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:07.86,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Please... don't let Nayu-chan hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.15,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:17.68,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Aren't your underwear a little mature today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:23.48,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't really know why, but I've started wanting to wear stuff like this lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:31.80,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you're in love with someone, Haruka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:32.66,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.01,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why do you ask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:41.65,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered that my grandma once told me that love and underwear are inseparable even if you tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:47.79,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,So I was wondering if you had fallen in love with someone since you changed your underwear style.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:50.86,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry if I was way off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:55.48,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:59.10,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the goldfish bite you somewhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:01.93,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:09.48,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I... might be in love with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.65,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.65,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.28,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I Lo-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.16,RM main 2,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.53,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-san, Shiraishi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:23.18,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,We're over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:26.71,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! Here, I brought you a towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.76,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I got a message from Keigo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.18,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,From Senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:37.30,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:38.57,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.77,RM main 2,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,You should go meet up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:40.98,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:41.35,RM main 2,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:44.34,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay. And Sensei's here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.82,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I can go if you li--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:47.48,RM main 2,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be right back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.94,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.49,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring me all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:03.93,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Sorry about this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:08.18,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,F-For showing you such pathetic underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.92,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.70,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you think about these underwear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.22,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.60,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:21.60,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.26,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd show their underwear off in front of a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.14,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are my childhood friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:29.94,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Yako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:31.89,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be more careful from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:34.22,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.76,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said some pretty terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:41.73,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to make things right in the text as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:42.78,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:46.78,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Cat-eyes was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:47.41,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.99,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're even!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:53.42,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go easy on you starting tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.09,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want it any other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:55.84,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.06,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:58.92,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:03.46,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,You should never let your guard down! That's the way of the warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.92,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Your leg's showing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.64,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:11.84,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:16.58,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I worked things out with Kota!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:19.07,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:21.95,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-san got lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.59,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Keigo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.93,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have missed each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.64,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,She's not answering her phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:33.00,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't cry Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:36.10,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, let's look for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:36.85,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:40.01,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, can't she do anything herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.93,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I was supposed to be keeping an eye on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.93,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.39,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:58.80,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay with you until your mom finds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.56,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a candied apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.12,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.21,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:08.99,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.80,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:17.06,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.67,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks are over...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:25.49,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,They do fireworks every year, so we can come together again next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:29.65,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,This year, and the year after next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:33.59,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to festivals with Nayu-chan and everyone else like this, even when we become adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:34.83,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:38.55,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, stop causing us so much trouble though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:39.33,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:41.48,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped my cellphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.06,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you just noticed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.13,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:48.66,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it! You're treating us all to chocolate bananas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.26,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:53.03,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,We went all the way to the lost and found for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:57.06,RM main,Note at top of screen,0000,0000,0000,,You've made some wonderful friends, Nayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.80,0:23:43.36,RM main,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Breasts apparently come in all shapes and sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:44.03,RM main,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:48.02,RM main,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,There are bell-shaped, plate-shaped, rock-shaped, and squash-shaped breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:50.10,RM main,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Like hanging squash?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.10,0:23:51.91,RM main,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want those no matter how big they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:54.19,RM main,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss out on the next episode of {\i1}Chu-bra{\i0}!
